<i>in Chicago.</i>

234
00:13:52.290 --> 00:13:54.667
They have murdered
Fred Hampton.

235
00:13:54.751 --> 00:13:56.586
They are out to murder me.

236
00:13:56.627 --> 00:13:57.712
<i>It's like they'll</i>
<i>murder anybody</i>

237
00:13:57.795 --> 00:14:00.256
<i>that's Black in this country.</i>

238
00:14:00.298 --> 00:14:02.925
<i>- Maurice was</i>
<i>part of a generation</i>

239
00:14:03.009 --> 00:14:08.181
