<i>of that. it fired Blacks up.</i>

245
00:14:25.156 --> 00:14:26.741
<i>For the quick solution.</i>

246
00:14:26.824 --> 00:14:28.868
<i>- On the South Side</i>
<i>of Chicago.</i>

247
00:14:28.951 --> 00:14:33.539
