Movement using Afrocentricity.

248
00:14:33.623 --> 00:14:38.711
<i>reimagining Blackness through</i>
<i>a connection to Africa.</i>

249
00:14:38.795 --> 00:14:41.005
<i>defining Blackness</i>
<i>on its own terms.</i>

250
00:14:45.051 --> 00:14:48.221
<i>- It kind of inspired me</i>
<i>to get a bead</i>

251
00:14:48.304 --> 00:14:50.807
