<i>around with it.</i>

254
00:14:58.898 --> 00:15:01.109
<i>- The kalimba</i>
<i>is the thumb piano</i>

255
00:15:01.150 --> 00:15:05.154
<i>used by some African poets.</i>
<i>storytellers.</i>

256
00:15:05.238 --> 00:15:09.283
keepers of history
for meaningful connections

257
00:15:09.367 --> 00:15:10.368
<i>in the universe.</i>

258
00:15:15.164 --> 00:15:17.917
<i>- One night.</i>
<i>when I was with Ramsey Lewis.</i>

259
00:15:18.000 --> 00:15:20.461
<i>I picked up the kalimba</i>
<i>and started to play.</i>

260
00:15:20.545 --> 00:15:22.422
<i>and they liked it.</i>

261
00:15:30.054 --> 00:15:33.266
<i>- That was amazing</i>
<i>because it brought me closer</i>

262
00:15:33.349 --> 00:15:37.687
to knowing more about
what I was so curious about.

263
00:15:37.728 --> 00:15:39.480
And that was Africa.

264
00:15:41.732 --> 00:15:42.984
Say. I'm gonna
teach you some very

265
