- Yes.

286
00:16:31.741 --> 00:16:33.242
All right.

287
00:16:33.284 --> 00:16:37.330
We had not heard
anything like that before.

288
00:16:38.831 --> 00:16:41.250
<i>You know. we are somebody.</i>

289
00:16:41.334 --> 00:16:44.837
We can feel good
about ourselves.

290
00:16:44.921 --> 00:16:48.633
It was feeding
into little souls like mine.

291
00:16:48.716 --> 00:16:51.302
<i>It was Black positivity.</i>

292
00:16:52.637 --> 00:16:55.806
<i>- For brothers and sisters.</i>
<i>it was a revolution.</i>

293
00:16:55.890 --> 00:16:58.100
It was just time to shine.

294
00:17:00.853 --> 00:17:06.067
<i>ﾃ｢邃｢ﾂｪ ﾃ｢邃｢ﾂｪ</i>

295
00:17:06.150 --> 00:17:09.695
<i>Hey. on a solo.</i>

296
00:17:09.779 --> 00:17:11.781
<i>- So I started having visions</i>
<i>of this group</i>

297
00:17:11.822 --> 00:17:16.953
<i>and create this music to see</i>
<i>ourselves in a different way.</i>

298
00:17:17.036 --> 00:17:19.622
<i>I was inspired</i>
<i>by reading a book</i>

299
00:17:19.664 --> 00:17:22.792
<i>called "Laws of Success"</i>
<i>by Napoleon Hill.</i>

300
00:17:30.132 --> 00:17:34.095
