to a new form of awareness.

301
00:17:34.178 --> 00:17:36.681
<i>positive thinking.</i>

302
00:17:36.764 --> 00:17:40.059
Whatever the mind can
conceive and believe.

303
00:17:40.142 --> 00:17:41.435
it can achieve.

304
00:17:41.519 --> 00:17:43.854
You're capable
of doing anything.

305
00:17:43.938 --> 00:17:45.982
Napoleon Hill said.
when you want

306
00:17:46.065 --> 00:17:48.985
to manifest something
into reality.

307
00:17:49.026 --> 00:17:50.528
<i>there is a process for it.</i>

308
00:17:51.904 --> 00:17:53.656
<i>Write it out clearly.</i>

309
00:17:53.739 --> 00:17:58.202
<i>Tell the mind what you want</i>
<i>over and over and over again.</i>

310
00:17:58.286 --> 00:18:01.831
<i>- It's like this thing kept</i>
<i>on formulating in my mind.</i>

311
00:18:04.458 --> 00:18:08.087
<i>I wanted to reach</i>
<i>a universal audience.</i>

312
00:18:10.214 --> 00:18:13.593
<i>To evolve consciousness</i>
<i>through the music.</i>

313
00:18:16.929 --> 00:18:18.556
<i>And change the world.</i>

314
00:18:20.891 --> 00:18:25.021
<i>I finally drew a picture</i>
<i>of my vision of this group.</i>

315
00:18:28.065 --> 00:18:31.110
<i>ﾃ｢邃｢ﾂｪ ﾃ｢邃｢ﾂｪ</i>

316
00:18:31.193 --> 00:18:34.196
<i>And that's what</i>
<i>I set out to do.</i>

317
00:18:34.280 --> 00:18:38.534
So he decided
to leave Ramsey Lewis.

318
00:18:38.576 --> 00:18:40.786
To give up
the height of success.

319
00:18:40.870 --> 00:18:47.668
