321
00:18:55.301 --> 00:18:56.677
<i>- You have</i>
<i>to follow your heart</i>

322
00:18:56.761 --> 00:18:59.430
<i>and follow what's</i>
<i>important for you.</i>

323
00:18:59.513 --> 00:19:03.934
<i>And don't be afraid</i>
<i>to do that. to take chances.</i>

324
00:19:07.688 --> 00:19:11.901
<i>- Maurice said. I wanna go out</i>
<i>to California to start a band.</i>

325
00:19:11.942 --> 00:19:14.236
