332
00:19:34.048 --> 00:19:35.091
There are countercultures.

333
00:19:35.132 --> 00:19:37.510
There are Black hippies now.

334
00:19:37.593 --> 00:19:39.303
<i>- Mostly new-age consciousness</i>

335
00:19:39.387 --> 00:19:42.348
<i>and eating right</i>
<i>and living right.</i>

336
00:19:42.431 --> 00:19:44.183
<i>- There was a health store.</i>
<i>so we used to</i>

337
00:19:44.266 --> 00:19:45.685
