all the time--

338
00:19:45.768 --> 00:19:48.354
<i>Organicville.</i>

339
00:19:48.437 --> 00:19:51.607
<i>- One day.</i>
<i>Maurice White came in.</i>

340
00:19:51.691 --> 00:19:52.817
<i>and we locked eyes.</i>

341
00:19:56.278 --> 00:20:00.199
And all of a sudden.
I heard music.

342
00:20:00.282 --> 00:20:02.451
And I got chills.

343
00:20:02.535 --> 00:20:08.999
And he flashed me his smile.
and it was over.

344
00:20:09.083 --> 00:20:11.961
<i>I told my mom. I met someone.</i>

345
00:20:12.044 --> 00:20:13.212
<i>She says. yeah?</i>

346
00:20:13.295 --> 00:20:15.256
Is he Jewish?

347
00:20:15.339 --> 00:20:17.216
And I laughed.

348
00:20:17.299 --> 00:20:21.095
I said. no. Mom.
he is not Jewish.

349
00:20:21.178 --> 00:20:23.889
<i>We were interested</i>
<i>in learning.</i>

350
00:20:23.973 --> 00:20:26.475
<i>continuously learning.</i>

351
00:20:27.768 --> 00:20:28.811
<i>- Yeah.</i>
<i>I was doing a lot of study</i>

352
00:20:28.853 --> 00:20:32.815
<i>about metaphysics.</i>
<i>outer space. and inner space.</i>

353
00:20:34.442 --> 00:20:36.986
<i>- Maurice was learning</i>
<i>that the universe</i>

354
00:20:37.027 --> 00:20:40.114
<i>is this one powerful force.</i>

355
00:20:40.197 --> 00:20:44.368
<i>But instead of looking up.</i>
<i>look in.</i>

356
00:20:44.452 --> 00:20:47.705
We are the vehicle in which
the power comes through.

357
00:20:50.458 --> 00:20:52.626
We exist now.
on this plane.

358
00:20:52.710 --> 00:20:54.837
