a physical plane.

359
00:20:57.381 --> 00:20:59.550
<i>But if you tune in</i>
<i>to the universe.</i>

360
00:20:59.633 --> 00:21:03.304
<i>you can more or less</i>
<i>elevate yourself consciously.</i>

361
00:21:06.182 --> 00:21:08.517
<i>- He told me</i>
<i>he wanted to bring</i>

362
00:21:08.601 --> 00:21:12.855
<i>that mysticism into his band.</i>

363
00:21:12.938 --> 00:21:14.231
