365
00:21:16.692 --> 00:21:18.694
<i>- I was into astrology</i>
<i>real heavy.</i>

366
00:21:18.736 --> 00:21:22.531
<i>And I was looking</i>
<i>at my astrological chart.</i>

367
00:21:22.573 --> 00:21:24.366
<i>I started to put</i>
<i>the elements together.</i>

368
00:21:24.450 --> 00:21:31.040
<i>And I had Earth in my chart.</i>
<i>fire in my chart. and air.</i>

369
00:21:31.081 --> 00:21:34.251
<i>And I changed air to wind.</i>
<i>and the rest is history.</i>

370
00:21:38.088 --> 00:21:40.549
Earth. Wind & Fire
is basically

371
00:21:40.591 --> 00:21:42.885
that of the true elements
of the universe.

372
00:21:42.927 --> 00:21:44.345
It just had a ring to it.

373
00:21:52.937 --> 00:21:54.730
<i>So I had three songwriters</i>

374
00:21:54.772 --> 00:21:56.524
